{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-20T18:25:06.042Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prompt chaining"},{"type":"text","text":" is a technique that breaks down complex tasks into a series of smaller, focused subtasks, where the output from one prompt becomes the input for the next."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"The core insight:"},{"type":"text","text":" Instead of asking an AI to complete a massive, complex task in one go, you "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"break it into sequential steps"},{"type":"text","text":" that build on each other."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why Chain Prompts: The 5 Key Benefits"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"1. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Handles Complex Tasks"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"By providing a clear direction and structure, prompt chaining helps the model to better understand the user's intentions and produce more accurate and relevant results."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prompt chaining improves task efficiency by breaking down complex problems into manageable steps, allowing large language models (LLMs) to handle multi-step workflows more effectively."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Without chaining:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"Write a complete marketing strategy for our new SaaS product including target audience analysis, competitive research, content plan, budget allocation, and metrics.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"→ AI may miss details, give generic advice, or produce inconsistent output."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"With chaining:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Step 1: \"Identify the target audience for a SaaS product in [industry]\"\nStep 2: \"Based on this audience [output from Step 1], analyze 3 key competitors\"\nStep 3: \"Using this audience and competitor data [output from Steps 1-2], create a content plan\"\nStep 4: \"Based on this content plan [output from Step 3], allocate budget across channels\"\nStep 5: \"Using this budget and strategy [output from Steps 1-4], define success metrics\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"→ Each step is focused, builds on previous context, and produces higher-quality output."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"2. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Reduces Errors"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prompt chaining offers a structured way to break down complex tasks into manageable steps, reducing errors and improving consistency across AI workflows."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Why it reduces errors:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- Smaller, focused tasks are easier to execute correctly\n- Each step can be reviewed and validated before moving forward\n- Errors are caught early in the chain, not at the end"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"3. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Improves Accuracy"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"By providing a clear direction and structure, prompt chaining helps the model to better understand the user's intentions and produce more accurate and relevant results."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prompt chaining breaks complex tasks into manageable, sequenced prompts for LLMs, increasing accuracy, transparency, and control."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"One-shot prompt:"},{"type":"text","text":" \"Summarize this 50-page document and extract key insights\" → May miss important details\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Chained prompts:"},{"type":"text","text":" 1. \"Summarize pages 1-10\" → Good summary 2. \"Summarize pages 11-20\" → Good summary 3. \"Summarize pages 21-30\" → Good summary 4. \"Combine all summaries into a final document\" → Comprehensive result"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"4. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Increases Transparency"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prompt chaining breaks complex tasks into manageable, sequenced prompts for LLMs, increasing accuracy, transparency, and control."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Why it increases transparency:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- You can see the reasoning process at each step\n- Each intermediate output is visible and auditable\n- You understand how the final answer was derived"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Without chaining:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"Should I invest in this stock?\"\n→ \"Yes, buy it.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You have no way to verify the reasoning."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"With chaining:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Step 1: \"What are the company's revenue trends?\" → \"Revenue grew 15% YoY\"\nStep 2: \"What is the profit margin?\" → \"22% profit margin\"\nStep 3: \"What is the competitor landscape?\" → \"Market leader with 35% share\"\nStep 4: \"Based on revenue, profit, and market position, should I invest?\" → \"Yes, the fundamentals are strong\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You can verify each piece of reasoning."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"5. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Improves Control"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prompt chaining breaks complex tasks into manageable, sequenced prompts for LLMs, increasing accuracy, transparency, and control."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Why it improves control:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- You can intervene at each step\n- You can adjust intermediate outputs before proceeding\n- You can stop the chain if something goes wrong"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Prompt Chaining vs. Chain of Thought"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This is a critical distinction that many people confuse:"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Aspect"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prompt Chaining"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Chain of Thought"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"What it is"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Multiple prompts in sequence (Prompt 1 → Output 1 → Prompt 2 → Output 2 →...)"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Single prompt with internal reasoning steps"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Structure"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Separate API calls or conversation turns"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"One response with "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"<thinking>"},{"type":"text","text":" tags or \"step-by-step\""}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Use case"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Multi-step workflows, content pipelines"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Complex reasoning, math, logic"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"1. \"Identify audience\" → 2. \"Create content plan based on audience\""}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"Let's think step by step: 1. Revenue = $50 × 2 = $100. 2. Discount = $100 × 0.20 = $20...\""}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Benefit"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Handles complex, multi-part tasks"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Improves accuracy on reasoning tasks"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[airops](https://www.airops.com/blog/prompt-chaining-vs-chain-of-thought)"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prompt chaining is a powerful technique that enhances content operations by breaking down larger tasks into a series of smaller, focused subtasks."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Chain-of-thought (CoT) prompting enables complex reasoning capabilities through intermediate reasoning steps within a single prompt."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Real-World Chaining Examples"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Example 1: "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Content Creation Pipeline"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Step 1: \"Research trending topics in [industry] for [target audience]\"\n→ Output: List of 5 trending topics\n\nStep 2: \"Based on these trending topics [output from Step 1], select the best one for a blog post\"\n→ Output: Selected topic + rationale\n\nStep 3: \"Using this topic [output from Step 2], write a blog post outline with 5 sections\"\n→ Output: Detailed outline\n\nStep 4: \"Based on this outline [output from Step 3], write the full blog post\"\n→ Output: Complete blog post\n\nStep 5: \"Review this blog post [output from Step 4] and suggest 3 improvements\"\n→ Output: Improvement suggestions"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Without chaining:"},{"type":"text","text":" \"Write a blog post about trending topics in\" → Generic, shallow content"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"With chaining:"},{"type":"text","text":" Comprehensive, well-researched, targeted content"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Example 2: "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Code Development Workflow"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Step 1: \"Analyze this codebase structure and identify the main components\"\n→ Output: List of components\n\nStep 2: \"Based on these components [output from Step 1], design a new feature for [functionality]\"\n→ Output: Feature design\n\nStep 3: \"Using this feature design [output from Step 2], write the implementation code\"\n→ Output: Implementation\n\nStep 4: \"Review this implementation [output from Step 3] for security vulnerabilities\"\n→ Output: Security analysis\n\nStep 5: \"Based on this security analysis [output from Step 4], fix any issues\"\n→ Output: Fixed implementation"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Example 3: "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Business Decision Support"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Step 1: \"What are the current market trends for [industry]?\"\n→ Output: Market trends analysis\n\nStep 2: \"Based on these market trends [output from Step 1], identify 3 opportunities for our company\"\n→ Output: List of opportunities\n\nStep 3: \"For each opportunity [output from Step 2], analyze the risks and benefits\"\n→ Output: Risk/benefit analysis\n\nStep 4: \"Based on this analysis [output from Step 3], recommend the best opportunity to pursue\"\n→ Output: Top recommendation\n\nStep 5: \"Create an implementation plan for this recommendation [output from Step 4]\"\n→ Output: Detailed plan"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"When to Use Prompt Chaining"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Use Prompt Chaining When:"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Scenario"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Complex tasks"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Multiple steps needed to complete the task"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Multi-step workflows"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sequential process required"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Content pipelines"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Need to build up content progressively"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Integration with external tools"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"AI needs to interact with APIs, databases, etc."}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Quality control"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Need to review intermediate outputs"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Long documents"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Can't process entire document in one prompt"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Research tasks"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Need to gather info → analyze → synthesize"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"❌ "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Don't Use Prompt Chaining When:"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Scenario"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Simple tasks"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"One prompt is sufficient"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Quick questions"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Single-turn response works"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Short content"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"No need for multi-step process"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Low-stakes decisions"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Transparency and control not critical"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Summary"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Why chain prompts:"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Handles complex tasks"},{"type":"text","text":" — Breaks down complex problems into manageable steps"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Reduces errors"},{"type":"text","text":" — Structured approach reduces errors and improves consistency"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Improves accuracy"},{"type":"text","text":" — Clear direction and structure produce more accurate results"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Increases transparency"},{"type":"text","text":" — Visible reasoning process at each step"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Improves control"},{"type":"text","text":" — Can intervene at each step and adjust intermediate outputs"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prompt chaining vs. Chain of Thought:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prompt Chaining:"},{"type":"text","text":" Multiple prompts in sequence (Prompt 1 → Prompt 2 → Prompt 3)\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Chain of Thought:"},{"type":"text","text":" Single prompt with internal reasoning steps (\"Let's think step by step\")"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"When to use prompt chaining:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- ✅ Complex tasks, multi-step workflows, content pipelines, external tool integration, quality control, long documents, research tasks\n- ❌ Simple tasks, quick questions, short content, low-stakes decisions"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prompt chaining breaks complex tasks into manageable, sequenced prompts for LLMs, increasing accuracy, transparency, and control."}]}]}}
